mMny kI giq khI n jwie ]
jo pRwnI swihb dI qwbydwrI krdw hY aus dI hwlq ibAwn nhIN kIqI jw skdI[
The state of the faithful cannot be described.
mMny kI = mMnx vwly dI, pqIjy hoey dI, XkIn kr lYx vwly dI[ giq = hwlq, AvsQw[
aus mnu`K dI (au~cI) Awqmk AvsQw d`sI nhIN jw skdI, ijs ny (Akwl purK dy nwm nUM) mMn ilAw hY, (Bwv, ijs dI lgn nwm ivc l`g geI hY)[

jy ko khY ipCY pCuqwie ]
jykr koeI jxw ibAwn krn dI koiSS krdw hY auh mgroN pCqwauNdw hY[
One who tries to describe this shall regret the attempt.
khY = d`sy, ibAwn kry[
jy koeI mnu`K ibAwn kry BI, qW auh ipCoN pCqwauNdw hY (ik mYN hoCw jqn kIqw hY)[

kwgid klm n ilKxhwru ]
koeI kwgz, lyKxI qy ilKwrI nhIN,
No paper, no pen, no scribe
kwgid = kwZz au~qy[ klm = klm (nwl)[
(nwm ivc) pqIjy hoey dI Awqmk AvsQw kwgz au~qy klm nwl koeI mnu`K ilKx dy smr`Q nhIN hY,

mMny kw bih krin vIcwru ]
ijs nwl bYT ky r`b dy Prmwbrdwr dI dSw ilKI jW socI ivcwrI jwvy[
can record the state of the faithful.
