(BwvyN ik mnu`K) rl ky aus dw AMdwzw lwaux bwbq vIcwr (zrUr) krdy hn[

AYsw nwmu inrMjnu hoie ]
ieho ijhw hY piv`qr pRBU dw nwm[
Such is the Name of the Immaculate Lord.
AYsw = Aijhw, ie`fw au~cw[ hoie = hY[ mMin = SrDw Dwr ky, lgn lw ky[
Akwl purK dw nwm bhuq (au~cw) hY qy mwieAw dy prBwv qoN pry hY, (ies ivc juVn vwlw BI au~cI Awqmk AvsQw vwlw ho jWdw hY, pr ieh g`l qW hI smJ iv`c AwauNdI hY)

jy ko mMin jwxY min koie ]12]
jykr koeI jxw r`b dI qwbydwrI kry, AYsw ivrlw jIv Awpxy ic`q AMdr hI aus dI KuSI nUM smJdw hY[
Only one who has faith comes to know such a state of mind. ||12||
mMin jwxY = SrDw r`K ky vyKy, mMn ky vyKy[ min = mn ivc[
